<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.1">
<l>uyyavu lakupaṭait tuṇṭama ṇivayiṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">vūḻitō ṟūḻipala vāliṉi laiyataṉmēl</l>
<l>paiyavi yōkutuyil koṇṭapa ramparaṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">paṅkaya nīṇayaṉat tañcaṉa mēṉiyaṉē</l>
<l>ceyyavaḷ niṉṉakalam cēmame ṉakkarutic</l>
<l rend="indent">celvupo limakarak kātuti kaḻntilaka</l>
<l>vaiyave ṉakkorukā lāṭuka ceṅkīrai</l>
<l rend="indent">yāyarkaḷ pōrēṟē yāṭuka vāṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with the sapphire stomach which [contains] the world</l>
<l rend="indent">that you created and consumed so that it would be saved,</l>
<l>Supreme Being who has gently slept the yogic sleep</l>
<l rend="indent">upon that banyan leaf for each of many successive aeons,</l>
<l>You with a body [the colour] of khol with wide lotus eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">having recalled that your chest is the refuge of the Red Lady,</l>
<l>Lord, please dance one time for me so that [your] ears</l>
<l rend="indent">[adorned with] Makara earrings abounding in riches, shine and shimmer.</l>
<l>Battle bull of the cowherds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
